machine_end_gcode:
G1 Z{z_offset+min(max_layer_z+10, printable_height)} F600 ; Move head up

G28 X ; home extruder on x-axis

M140 S0 ; turn off heatbed
M104 S0 T0 ; turn off hotend
M104 S0 T1 ; turn off hotend
M107 ; turn off fan
M84 X Y E ; disable motors
machine_start_gcode:
M605 S1 ; Auto-Park Mode
G90 ; use absolute coordinates
M83 ; extruder relative mode
M413 S0 ; disable power-loss recovery

M140 S{bed_temperature_initial_layer[initial_extruder]} ; start heating bed

; Start heating nozzles (not fully, or 0 if not used)
M104 S{(is_extruder_used[0] ? nozzle_temperature_initial_layer[0]-50 : 0)} T0
M104 S{(is_extruder_used[1] ? nozzle_temperature_initial_layer[1]-50 : 0)} T1

G28 X ; home x to buckets

M190 S{bed_temperature_initial_layer[initial_extruder]} ; wait for bed temp to stabilize

M280 P0 S160 ; Reset BL/CR Touch
G34 ; z stepper auto-align
G28 ; home all axis
G28 X ; home extruder on x-axis (to the buckets)
M420 S1 ; enable bed leveling

; Start heating all used nozzles to final temp (or 0 if not used)
M104 S{(is_extruder_used[0] ? nozzle_temperature_initial_layer[0] : 0)} T0
M104 S{(is_extruder_used[1] ? nozzle_temperature_initial_layer[1] : 0)} T1

G1 Z2.0 F3000 ; Move Z Axis down near bed

{if is_extruder_used[0]}
; LEFT EXTRUDER INIT
T0
M109 S{first_layer_temperature[0]} T0; wait for nozzle temp to stabilize
G92 E0 ; Reset Extruder
G1 X0.5 Y20 Z0.3 F5000.0 ; Move to start position
G1 X0.5 Y200.0 Z0.3 F1500.0 E14 ; Draw the first line
G1 X1 Y200.0 Z0.3 F5000.0 ; Move to side a little
G1 X1 Y20 Z0.3 F1500.0 E14 ; Draw the second line
G1 E-4.95 F1200 ; Retract
M104 S{nozzle_temperature_initial_layer[0]-50} T0 ;cooldown
G1 Z2.0 F3000 ; Move Z Axis up little to prevent scratching of Heat Bed
G28 X ; home to bucket - wipe
{endif}

{if is_extruder_used[1]}
; RIGHT EXTRUDER INIT
T1
M109 S{first_layer_temperature[1]} T1; wait for nozzle temp to stabilize
G92 E0 ; Reset Extruder
G1 X299.5 Y20 Z0.3 F5000.0 ; Move to start position
G1 X299.5 Y200.0 Z0.3 F1500.0 E14 ; Draw the first line
G1 X299 Y200.0 Z0.3 F5000.0 ; Move to side a little
G1 X299 Y20 Z0.3 F1500.0 E14 ; Draw the second line
G1 E-4.95 F1200 ; Retract
M104 S{nozzle_temperature_initial_layer[1]-50} T1 ;cooldown
G1 Z2.0 F3000 ; Move Z Axis up little to prevent scratching of Heat Bed
G28 X ; home to bucket - wipe
{endif}
name: SV04 Single and Dual
